playstore_details.title: HooplaKidz Plus Preschool App
playstore_details.description:
HooplaKidz Plus is a complete preschool edutainment app! Featuring safe kids videos that children and parents can enjoy commercial-free. Let your kids discover exciting new adventures in a magical world of fun and learning in a safe environment!

KID-FRIENDLY, FUN AND EDUCATIONAL CONTENT!

Kid shows: Watch the popular show The Adventures of Annie & BenKid songs: Sing along to classic songs like Old MacDonald to new songs like Baby Shark and more!Early learning videos: Kids can learn numbers, colors, fruits, alphabets and more!Fun activities: Children can learn how to draw, play dough, cook and fun science experiments!

New videos to be introduced every month!

HOOPLAKIDZ PLUS FEATURES:

• 100% kids-safe!
• No ads, fully commercial-free!
• Watch offline! Easy Download & Go option!
• COPPA compliant
• Curated by expert child-psychologists
• A complete family entertainment app
• New HooplaKidz videos exclusively on HooplaKidz Plus
• Single-subscription for full-access to all content and features on any device, anywhere

To access all features and content you can subscribe to HooplaKidz Plus on a monthly or yearly basis with an auto-renewing subscription right inside the app.* Pricing can vary by region and will be confirmed before purchase in the app. In app subscriptions will automatically renew at the end of their cycle.

All payments will be paid through your Google Account and may be managed under Account Settings after the initial payment. Subscription payments will automatically renew unless deactivated at least 24-hours before the end of the current cycle. Your account will be charged for renewal at least 24-hours prior to the end of the current cycle. Any unused portion of your free trial will be forfeited upon payment. Cancellations are incurred by disabling auto-renewal.

Terms of Service: https://plus.hooplakidz.com/tos
Privacy Policy: https://plus.hooplakidz.com/privacy
